If you’re intrigued by the Democracy Game, getting started is straightforward:Join Farcaster: Visit farcaster.xyz to sign up and explore the platform.

Find the Democracy Game Channel: Navigate to https://farcaster.xyz/~/channel/democracygame to join the conversation.
Engage and Experiment: Participate in proposals, vote on ideas, or start discussions about governance.
Learn More: Check out docs.farcaster.xyz for technical details on how Farcaster works and how you can build on it.

For developers interested in creating similar experiments, Farcaster’s documentation offers guides on building mini-apps, syncing data with Snapchain nodes, and more.

